Handling checkboxes and radiobuttons:
-- if you have only one checkbox or radiobutton -- you can simply click on it
-- if you have multiple checkboxes or radiobuttons -- store them in a list and loop through

DropDowns
--Dropdown is a menu which allows you to select one or multiple options

    Types:
        1. Single select
        2. Multiple select

    Handling dropdowns:
        1. click on the dropdown, click on the option
        2. using a select class:
            -- in order to use select class we need to make sure we have a <select> tag in html

    Selecting options from dropdown can be done in 3 ways:
        1. by index
        2. by visible text
        3. by value

    In order to deselect options from dropdown we can use the following methods:
    -- your DD must be multiple select
        1. deselectByIndex()
        2. deselectByVisibleText()
        3. deselectByValue()
        4. deselectAll()